                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <desc>
                    These are two quires from one book: Quire 1 is a balanced quire comprised of four sheet, 8 folios. Quire 2 is comprised of 12 folios, but several are half sheets and the final architecture of the quire is unclear. The manuscript has been disbound and assembled in disorder, as the list of contents makes clear
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <locus target="#8v" facs="009">Fol. 8v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Blank
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                  </list>
